# Frontend (Vite) — variables must be present at `npm run build` on Render (not runtime).
#
# Local dev: leave unset to use relative `/api` (Vite dev server proxies to the backend).
# Production: set to your deployed API (HTTPS), e.g. https://YOUR-API.onrender.com/api
#
# VITE_API_URL=https://YOUR-API.onrender.com/api
